'''Kashnir Arms''' was a small arms manufacturer which sprung up around the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. When many of their weapons were found in the hands of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|ISB]] agents were sent to investigate the company. Soon after, both Kashnir Arms factories were shut down and their major production equipment was loaded into [[Freighter/Legends|freighters]] and lifted off [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. Some time after this, it was revealed that the company had been largely owned by influential Alliance supporters through a front corporation. It was later discovered, when the [[KX-80 repeating blaster rifle]] came into production, that Kashnir Arms had once again started operating, this time under Alliance direction.

